The paper deals with the topic of automated learning in relational domains using neural networks, which falls under the broad category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The use of neural networks and the focus on predictive power suggests that the paper could also be classified under Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with natural language processing tasks, such as sentiment analysis, which falls under Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The use of relational domains and the focus on Horn clauses suggests that the paper could also be classified under Databases (cs.DB). Finally, the paper deals with the use of deep neural networks, which falls under Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
